279
00:14:22.379 --> 00:14:24.397
<i>Ecco qua, bello.</i>

280
00:14:28.536 --> 00:14:30.836
- Mamma.
- Solo un secondo, tesoro.


281
00:14:31.923 --> 00:14:32.973
Sono Sarah.

282
00:14:34.443 --> 00:14:38.285
<i>Sedona, Arizona.

283
00:14:54.792 --> 00:14:58.073
Grazie per essere giunta qui
